YoungAdultsdf = combineddf[(combineddf['Age of Customer'] >=18) & (combineddf['Age of Customer'] <=25)]  
YA_profitpercustomer = YoungAdultsdf['Total Profit'].sum() / YoungAdultsdf['Customer ID'].count()
YA_Average_Repeat_Purchases = YoungAdultsdf['Subsequent Orders Count'].sum() / YoungAdultsdf['Customer ID'].count()   
YA_promotions_utulized = YoungAdultsdf['Total value of all promotions'].sum() / YoungAdultsdf['Customer ID'].count() 
YA_rentention_slice = YoungAdultsdf[YoungAdultsdf['Subsequent Orders Count'] > 0].copy()
YA_rentention_rate =  (YA_rentention_slice['Subsequent Orders Count'].count() / YoungAdultsdf['Customer ID'].count()) * 100
print(f'Average Amount of Subsequent Orders for Young Adult Customers: {YA_Average_Repeat_Purchases}') 
print(f'Profit Per Young Adult Customer: {YA_profitpercustomer}')   
print(f'Average Amount of Promotions Utulized for Young Adult Customers: {YA_promotions_utulized}') 
print(f'Retention Rate for Young Adult Customers: {YA_rentention_rate}')
numofYAdultCust = YoungAdultsdf.groupby('Source of Customer')['Customer ID'].count()   
percent_of_YA_customers  = (numofYAdultCust / YoungAdultsdf['Customer ID'].count()) * 100   
YA_Sourcedf = pd.concat([numofYAdultCust, percent_of_YA_customers], axis= 1) 
YA_Sourcedf = YA_Sourcedf.reset_index() 
YA_Sourcedf.columns = ['Source of Customer', 'Number of Customers', 'Percentage of Customers']  
YA_Sourcedf['Percentage of Customers'] = YA_Sourcedf['Percentage of Customers'].apply(lambda x: f'{x:,.2f}%')  
YA_Sourcedf.head()
